$123.0 million in aggregate principal amount of Solar Loan-backed Notes, Series 2017-A, Class A; $8.8 million in aggregate
principal amount of Solar Loan-backed Notes, Series 2017-A, Class B, and $13.2 million in aggregate principal amount of Solar
Loan-backed Notes, Series 2017-A, Class C, backed by these notes receivable to investors. The SPE is wholly owned by us and is
consolidated in the financial statements. Accordingly, we did not recognize a gain or loss on the transfer of these notes receivable.
