aggregate principal amount of Automotive Asset-backed Notes, Series 2018-A, backed by these automotive assets to investors. The
SPE is wholly owned by us and is consolidated in the financial statements. The proceeds from the issuance, net of discounts and
fees, were $543.1 million. The cash flows generated by these automotive assets are used to service the monthly principal and
interest payments on the Automotive Asset-backed Notes and satisfy the SPE’s expenses, and any remaining cash is distributed to
