with our revenue recognition policy. The SPE’s assets and cash flows are not available to our other creditors, and the creditors of
the SPE, including the Automotive Asset-backed Note holders, have no recourse to our other assets. A third-party contracted with
us to provide administrative and collection services for these automotive assets.
